
The iF Design Award 2022 is now open for submissions. First awarded in 1953, the iF Design Award is the oldest independent design seal in the world. It is a symbol of outstanding design achievements that focuses on the innovative power of design.
The award categories include Product, Packaging, Communication, Service Design, User Experience (UX), User Interface (UI), Architecture and Interior Architecture.

The deadline for submissions is October 15, with a late deadline of November 19, 2021.

for more details: ifworlddesignguide.com

